{
  "stem": "15393.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In those days, people were still working in their own capacities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They lived in their flats or apartments, if you like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They, they were not really handicapped very badly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was rationing, but not too bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In other words, one didn't know-- what is it all about?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why is it that they're talking such terrible things about these Germans?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not so bad at all-- they're letting us live.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're letting us live quite decently.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what we heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the other hand, from Russia, the letters that were coming from Russia were horrors, horror stories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were starving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were in Siberia in terrible, terrible conditions and terrible climatic conditions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They needed food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They needed this, they needed-- they were not dressed adequately.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were sending parcels to Russia, while we were occupied by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the other side, in Germany, everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the Germans came, we didn't know what to expect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were hoping that, hopefully, we should somehow be able to, to survive that, however long this occupation will take.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But slowly, slowly, things were not so good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, what I did not mention-- maybe I should have mentioned that when the Russians came-- I'll go back for a moment.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the Russians came in, immediately, almost immediately, they disposed with practically the entire intelligentsia in Lwow-- professorships, you know; professors; doctors; of course, officers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Professional officers were taken away and killed, were taken to prisons, tortured, but mostly killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The intelligentsia went immediately.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They disposed of it, exactly as the Germans did with-- when they came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the first thing they did, disposed with the hierarchy of the-- not only Jewish, also Polish, also Polish, not only Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
